snippet.title: Interton VC 4000 - Carts 1-20 (1978) - gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Interton © 1978 
[Computer] Interton VC-4000
Emulator:  MESS / MAME
Intro Song:  "Spectrum" (2012) - by Zedd

Here's a quick overview of the first 20 cartridges released for the Interton VC-4000 system.  About 40 were released overall, so I've just grouped them into 20 that I will cover for 1978 and 20 more I'll cover when we hit 1979.

Cart 01: Grand Prix
Cart 02: Blackjack 
Cart 03: Olympics 
Cart 04: Combat
Cart 05: Basic Math 1
Cart 06: Math 2 - Multiplication/Division + and -
Cart 07: Air/Sea Battle
Cart 08: Treasure Hunt
Cart 09: Super Maze
Cart 10: Winter Sports
Cart 11: Horse Racing
Cart 12:  Shooting Gallery
Cart 13:  Chess
Cart 14: Motorcross
Cart 15: Four-In-A-Row (Intelligence II)
Cart 16: Mastermind
Cart 17: Circus
Cart 18:  Boxing
Cart 19:  Space War
Cart 20:  Musical Games
